Class IntegralSensor

java.lang.Object
  sensors.Sensor
      sensors.IntegralSensor

public abstract class IntegralSensor
extends Sensor

An integral sensor (only provides integral values) which is easily extensible by more specific sensors.

Author:
Colin Poler
